<p class="line">
<br>
<p class="title"><span class="title-box">Operation 21O:
– </span></p><p class="para"></span></p><p class="para">There is a delay in our scheduled correspondence from the
Council of Humanity. All communication personnel should carry out
designated confirmation protocols.</p>
<br>
<p class="title"><span class="title-box">Operation 6O:
– </span></p><p class="para">Hmm... I feel like there's a lot of noise mixed in with this
data. I wonder what it is? ... Wait. This isn't noise.</p>
<br>
<p class="title"><span class="title-box">Operation 21O:
– </span></p><p class="para"></span></p><p class="para">Commencing scan. If you don't get anything after four seconds,
try a pattern comparison.</p>
<br>
<p class="title"><span class="title-box">Operation 6O:
– </span></p><p class="para">Hold on. This was in a message from the council...</p>
<br>
<p class="title"><span class="title-box">Operation 21O:
– </span></p><p class="para"></span></p><p class="para">The Commander... Contact the Commander! Hurry!</p>
<br>
<p class="title"><span class="title-box">Operation 6O:
– </span></p><p class="para">I can't! All the ports have been destroyed, and...</p>
<br>
<p class="para"><i>The
stage flashes red. The word Error appears on the screen while a siren
goes off.</i></p>
<br>
<p class="para">[Maniacal
laughter]</p>
<br>
<p class="title"><span class="title-box">Operation 21O:
– </span></p><p class="para"></span></p><p class="para">The infection is...</p>
<br>
<p class="title"><span class="title-box">Operation 6O:
– </span></p><p class="para">No... Noooooo!</p>
<p class="line">
<br>
<p class="para">-Crumbling
Lies-</p>
<br>
<p class="para">June
26, 11945 
</p>
<br>
<p class="para">1:12
AM: Logic virus outbreak occurs within the Bunker satellite base.</p>
<p class="para">1:23
AM: Virus spreads to the Information Control Team.</p>
<p class="para">1:25
AM: All external communication channels are cut off.</p>
<p class="para">1:47
AM: Firefights between maintenance workers break out in the hangar.</p>
<p class="para">1:49
AM: Nearly all YoRHa members are infected.</p>
<p class="para">2:05
AM: Infected YoRHa members wreak havoc in the command room.</p>
<p class="para">2:18
AM: Fires break out in multiple living quarters.</p>
<p class="para">2:20
AM: An explosion occurs near the Bunker's fusion reactor.</p>
<p class="para">2:28
AM: YoRHa units 2B and 9S escape the Bunker.</p>
<p class="para">2:30
