<p class="title"><span class="title-box">Nier (narration):</span></p><p class="para">With their consciousness rearranged as data. 9S and
the others are sent into the small port. As their bodies gradually
vanish, the warm shrine welcomes a new visitor: tranquility.</p>
<br>
<p class="para"><p class="title"><span class="title-box">Mama:</span></p><p class="para"> Right! Let's get going too, shall we?</p>
