<p class="title"><span class="title-box">Nier (narration):</span></p><p class="para">Mama leads 2B and the Boy outside. The city's
collapse continues with ever-increasing intensity, yet strangely,
there is no sorrow here. All that exists is the clear, refreshing air
that surrounds them. 2B stops and gazes up at the white, cloudless
