Memories possessing eternal value. Memories which, while trivial,
have been gathered up and stored like the most precious of treasures.</p>
<br>
<p class="title"><span class="title-box">2B:
</span></p><p class="para">Thank you...</p>
<br>
<p class="title"><span class="title-box">Nier (narration):</span></p><p class="para">The words she whispers are absorbed by the open sky
as they quietly fade away.</p>
